{"tid":396661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警深井村抄牌被圍　5男女涉阻差辦公被捕","createTime":"2017-09-11T23:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T08:44:24.000Z","uid":81228,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03ba46d2193243173f350f1f88b0435338f9829e","tid":396661,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T23:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170912/photo/bkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170912070658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170912%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170912070658&h=39b717ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在深井村向違泊私家車發出告票。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<br />\n深井村因違例泊車觸發警民衝突，5男女被捕。案發於昨晚11時許，警方接獲市民投訴，指上址有車輛違例泊車，警員到場採取行動時，遭10多人包圍起哄，聲稱要與警員理論，警員向上峰增援，多輛警車接報趕至，控制場面，事件擾攘近2小時。警方經調查後，4男1女涉嫌「阻礙警務人員執行職務」及「公眾地方行為不檢」被捕，當中被捕女子更被揭發疑因欠交罰款遭通緝，5人被帶署扣查。東網記者到場，發現深井村近牌坊有警員向違泊私家車發出告票。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170912/photo/bkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170912070658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170912%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170912070658&h=61a9bec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員向違泊私家車抄牌。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170912/photo/bkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170912070658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170912%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170912070658&h=e08cdbe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案發於深井村。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170912/photo/bkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170912070658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170912%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170912070658&h=d194ec94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n違泊私家車被警員抄牌。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170912/bkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170912%2Fbkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001.html&d=B095%2B7ONDbWzZWxw%2F2Nrj7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a50403a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170912/bkn-20170912023704610-0912_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"15b3994fd7db0b1c43b5008fc358d75b58d77fa8","tid":396661,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:14:56.000Z","msg":"抵死<br />\n做野除帽"},{"pid":"286e80e14f57fd0034f00602ea02bbf4fa8ec609","tid":396661,"uid":53575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:23:17.000Z","msg":"G峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dca798f64a40554bc8699d6158d926b523bc06","tid":396661,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:49:50.000Z","msg":"警棍無雙呀嘛"},{"pid":"dcfe1420f8dfca069ea8976b6379d853bafaea41","tid":396661,"uid":9119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:55:37.000Z","msg":"支持警方嚴正執法"},{"pid":"5eef81183afcd81c693dbf13d8d6109b0eaa0724","tid":396661,"uid":38757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:07:09.000Z","msg":"有時我都見D 車真係太過分<br />\n泊還泊, 泊到係普通人都過唔到條路....."},{"pid":"fbf594c46bd917175ab1565c698bea3f9f3693de","tid":396661,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:09:49.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬大戰黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c9bc5476335cbbfea3925e861a4e558af24d9c","tid":396661,"uid":28767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時我都見D 車真係太過分<br />\n泊還泊, 泊到係普通人都過唔到條路.....</blockquote><br />\n題外話<br />\n見過有車泊上行人路 完全封死<br />\n行人如果要過就一定要經馬路兜過<br />\n仲要唔只一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"